The paper deals with deep learning-based 3D face reconstruction, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a novel loss function for weakly supervised learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with multi-image face reconstruction, which involves graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper uses deep neural networks, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
